# Calendly

In order to create this action, you would first need to integrate with your Calendly account.

<Frame>
  <img src="https://mintcdn.com/chatbase/DIWSTyTSabxfVW3B/user-guides/chatbot/images/actions/actions-39.gif?s=16d5b75fb36bc979abf7b15f12492c4c" alt="Chatbase Embed Code Example" width="800" height="460" data-path="user-guides/chatbot/images/actions/actions-39.gif" />
</Frame>

Once connected go to the Actions tab and select the "Calendly Get Slots" Action.

<Frame>
  <img src="https://mintcdn.com/chatbase/DIWSTyTSabxfVW3B/user-guides/chatbot/images/actions/actions-40.gif?s=6584d01cb3d412a757d0fbb98034d6a5" alt="Chatbase Embed Code Example" width="800" height="460" data-path="user-guides/chatbot/images/actions/actions-40.gif" />
</Frame>

Next select the Event from the dropdown that you want your Agent to use for bookings.

