  <img src="https://mintcdn.com/chatbase/DIWSTyTSabxfVW3B/user-guides/chatbot/images/actions/actions-41.gif?s=dccfa053b46294bce82d80fbfc290c92" alt="Chatbase Embed Code Example" width="800" height="460" data-path="user-guides/chatbot/images/actions/actions-41.gif" />
